name: Ultimecia
abilities: Ultimecia cannot be chosen by your opponent's Summons.

When Ultimecia enters the field, remove up to 5 Characters of cost 5 or more in your Break Zone from the game. When you removed 1 or more cards, choose the same number of Characters as the cards you removed this way. *Dull* them and *Freeze* them. You opponent discards 1 card.
